{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "0.560", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Pr\u00e4sidentin! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "0.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "1.320", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "1.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "2.840", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bereits die Wortwahl in dieser Debatte ist verwirrend und erweckt einen v\u00f6llig falschen Eindruck. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "2.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "4.280", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Grundgesetz legt klare Zust\u00e4ndigkeiten und somit Verantwortlichkeiten fest. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "4.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "5.520", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Grundgesetz ist dabei gepr\u00e4gt von einer Kooperationskultur zwischen Bund und L\u00e4ndern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "5.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.960", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die bereits Ausfluss des sogenannten Bundesstaatsprinzips ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "7.000", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es wird hier der Eindruck erweckt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "7.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "7.120", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der Bund w\u00fcrde die Bundesl\u00e4nder im Bereich der Bildung nicht oder nur unzureichend unterst\u00fctzen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "7.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "7.121", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und das ist schlichtweg falsch."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "7.121", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "7.680", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bund und L\u00e4nder kooperieren beispielsweise im Wissenschaftsbereich mit diversen Bund-L\u00e4nder-Vereinbarungen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "7.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "7.880", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "gemeinsamen Initiativen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "7.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.200", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Forschungseinrichtungen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.440", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Forschungsverb\u00fcnden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "10.720", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wobei der Verfassungsgeber bei der Reform von Artikel\u00a091b des Grundgesetzes im Jahr\u00a02014 ganz klar gesagt hat, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "10.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.320", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass es sich hierbei nicht um ein Instrument des Finanzausgleichs handelt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.840", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch im Bildungsbereich findet umfangreiche Bundesunterst\u00fctzung statt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.760", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Kollege Kaufmann hat Ihnen das vorhin schon n\u00e4hergebracht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.000", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Erfolgsprogramm des BMBF \u201eKultur macht stark. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.120", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "B\u00fcndnisse f\u00fcr Bildung\u201c, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.480", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das gerade frisch verl\u00e4ngert wurde, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "15.840", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "umfasst 230\u00a0Millionen Euro. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "15.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "16.440", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In meinem Wahlkreis werden dar\u00fcber alle au\u00dferschulischen Bildungsangebote bereitgestellt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "16.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "16.760", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Insgesamt stellt der Bund 5,7\u00a0Milliarden Euro an Finanzhilfen f\u00fcr die Bildungsinfrastruktur zur Verf\u00fcgung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "16.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "18.320", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das bedeutet f\u00fcr mein Heimatland Th\u00fcringen 70\u00a0Millionen Euro Bundesgelder f\u00fcr Schulbauten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "18.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "19.120", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dazu kommen Milliardenbetr\u00e4ge, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "19.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "19.600", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die der Bund f\u00fcr den Kitaausbau leistet. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "19.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "20.200", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Von 2008 bis 2020 sind das 12\u00a0Milliarden Euro."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "20.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "20.280", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "20.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.520", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Gelder werden von den L\u00e4ndern sogar nur unzureichend abgerufen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.680", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil es so viel ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.080", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bis zum 31.\u00a0Juli 2017 wurden lediglich 40\u00a0Prozent der Mittel des dritten Investitionsprogramms von den L\u00e4ndern abgerufen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.520", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "So viel nur dazu, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.521", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Suding, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.521", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.040", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil Sie sagten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.080", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "es sei zu wenig Geld da. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.081", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es scheint zu viel Geld da zu sein. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.081", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.082", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Man kann gar nicht alles verbauen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.082", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.083", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Qualit\u00e4tsoffensive Lehrerbildung hat Stefan Kaufmann genannt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.083", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.084", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bund-L\u00e4nder-Vereinbarungen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.084", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.085", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "500\u00a0Millionen Euro. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.085", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.086", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kommunales Bildungsmanagement: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.086", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.087", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "170\u00a0Millionen Euro. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.087", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.088", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In jedem Landkreis wird ein Bildungsmanager vom Bund finanziert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.088", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.089", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich denke, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.089", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.090", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das macht deutlich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.090", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "26.040", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie gut hier die Zusammenarbeit funktioniert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "26.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "26.600", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Digitalpakt wurde angesprochen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "26.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "27.040", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Er gilt auch f\u00fcr Berufsschulen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "27.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "28.360", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben verschiedene Rechtsgrundlagen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "28.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "29.560", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie wir diese mehr als 5\u00a0Milliarden Euro in die L\u00e4nder bringen k\u00f6nnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "29.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "29.720", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie sehen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "29.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.120", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bildung ist bereits eine gesamtstaatliche Aufgabe. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.680", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie wird gesamtstaatlich finanziert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "33.600", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Bund sorgt mit Milliardenzahlungen daf\u00fcr, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "33.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.800", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass gleichwertige Lebensverh\u00e4ltnisse in Deutschland entstehen und vorhanden sind. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.801", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dennoch wird hier behauptet, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.801", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.640", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Bundesl\u00e4nder w\u00e4ren mit ihrer Verantwortung \u00fcberfordert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.880", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch das ist falsch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.881", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.881", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.882", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist ein hausgemachtes Problem; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.882", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.883", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn es liegt an den Bundesl\u00e4ndern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.883", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "37.120", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ihre Mittel entsprechend einzusetzen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "37.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "37.240", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie m\u00fcssen sie da einsetzen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "37.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "37.720", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wo sie Verantwortung tragen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "37.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.040", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Stefan Kaufmann hat die massiven Steuermehreinnahmen der L\u00e4nder angesprochen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.480", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Brechen wir diese Milliardenbetr\u00e4ge einmal auf ein relativ\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.481", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in Anf\u00fchrungszeichen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.481", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.482", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "armes Bundesland wie Th\u00fcringen herunter: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.482", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.483", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Steuermehreinnahmen 2014: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.483", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.484", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "9\u00a0Millionen Euro, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.484", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.485", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "2015: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.485", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.486", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "48\u00a0Millionen Euro, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.486", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.487", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "2016: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.487", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.488", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "237\u00a0Millionen Euro, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.488", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.489", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "2017: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.489", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.490", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "348\u00a0Millionen Euro. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.490", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.491", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.491", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.492", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das sind Mehreinnahmen on top f\u00fcr den laufenden Haushalt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.492", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.493", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bei solchen Zahlen k\u00f6nnen Sie uns nicht erz\u00e4hlen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.493", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.494", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Th\u00fcringen k\u00f6nne seiner Bildungsverantwortung nicht gerecht werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.494", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.495", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich will Ihnen sagen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.495", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.496", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was in Th\u00fcringen los ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.496", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.497", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Genosse Bodo Ramelow nimmt lieber 39\u00a0Millionen Euro und saniert damit ein Fu\u00dfballstadion in Erfurt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.497", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.498", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um seinem Genossen Oberb\u00fcrgermeister einen Gefallen zu tun, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.498", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.499", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "anstatt dieses Geld verantwortungsvoll in Schulen und Hochschulen zu investieren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.499", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.500", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kollege Schipanski, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.500", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.501", 
   "id": "s000087", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "gestatten Sie eine Zwischenfrage?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.501", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.502", 
   "id": "s000088", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.502", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.503", 
   "id": "s000089", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir machen das am Ende mit einer Kurzintervention."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.503", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.504", 
   "id": "s000090", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das muss Kollegin Esken dann selbst entscheiden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.504", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.505", 
   "id": "s000091", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ob sie eine Kurzintervention machen m\u00f6chte."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.505", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.506", 
   "id": "s000092", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.506", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.507", 
   "id": "s000093", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der Bund ist keine zu melkende Kuh. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.507", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.508", 
   "id": "s000094", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Am 1.\u00a0Juni 2017 haben wir in diesem Hause einen neuen Bund-L\u00e4nder-Finanzausgleich beschlossen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.508", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.509", 
   "id": "s000095", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und zwar bei massiver Belastung des Bundes, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.509", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.510", 
   "id": "s000096", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der ab 2020 j\u00e4hrlich rund 10\u00a0Milliarden Euro mehr an die L\u00e4nder transferiert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.510", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.511", 
   "id": "s000097", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Sektkorken haben nach diesem Beschluss in allen deutschen Staatskanzleien geknallt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.511", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "41.960", 
   "id": "s000098", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der damalige Bundesfinanzminister Wolfgang Sch\u00e4uble verteidigte die Reform, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "41.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "42.320", 
   "id": "s000099", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "r\u00e4umte aber ein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "42.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "42.800", 
   "id": "s000100", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "es sei kein unproblematischer Schritt\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "42.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "42.880", 
   "id": "s000101", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zitat\u00a0\u2013:"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "42.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "43.920", 
   "id": "s000102", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir \u00e4ndern ein St\u00fcck weit die Architektur unserer f\u00f6deralen Finanzordnung."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "43.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "44.720", 
   "id": "s000103", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir sind ein Bundesstaat."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "44.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "46.800", 
   "id": "s000104", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Hamburgs regierender B\u00fcrgermeister Olaf Scholz sprach von einem guten Ergebnis f\u00fcr den deutschen F\u00f6deralismus\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "46.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "46.801", 
   "id": "s000105", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zitat\u00a0\u2013:"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "46.801", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "47.640", 
   "id": "s000106", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die 16\u00a0L\u00e4nder werden ihre Aufgaben wahrnehmen k\u00f6nnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "47.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "47.960", 
   "id": "s000107", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und sie werden es in enger Kooperation mit dem Bund tun."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "47.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "48.440", 
   "id": "s000108", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kollege Rossmann, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "48.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "48.680", 
   "id": "s000109", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ich frage mich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "48.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "48.880", 
   "id": "s000110", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "warum sich die SPD beschwert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "48.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "49.640", 
   "id": "s000111", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn Herr Scholz so spricht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "49.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.760", 
   "id": "s000112", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bund-L\u00e4nder-Finanzbeziehungen hei\u00dft n\u00e4mlich Fairness in der Finanzierung."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "52.280", 
   "id": "s000113", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im \u00dcbrigen sehen Sie das gro\u00dfe Interesse der L\u00e4nder an der vorgeschlagenen Grundgesetz\u00e4nderung heute hier auf der Bundesratsbank."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "52.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "52.360", 
   "id": "s000114", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "52.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "52.680", 
   "id": "s000115", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "des Pudels Kern im deutschen Schulsystem ist nicht die Frage, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "52.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "52.800", 
   "id": "s000116", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ob Bund, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "52.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "53.640", 
   "id": "s000117", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Land oder Kommune eine Schultoilette repariert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "53.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "54.120", 
   "id": "s000118", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Des Pudels Kern ist die Frage, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "54.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "55.520", 
   "id": "s000119", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "warum der Sch\u00fcler in Bremen hinsichtlich seines Wissens fast zwei Jahre hinter den Sch\u00fclern in Bayern hinterherhinkt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "55.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "55.760", 
   "id": "s000120", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist das Hauptproblem. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "55.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "55.761", 
   "id": "s000121", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist die eigentliche Frage bez\u00fcglich der Chancengerechtigkeit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "55.761", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "55.762", 
   "id": "s000122", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "welche wir mit vermeintlichen Bundesgeldern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "55.762", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "55.763", 
   "id": "s000123", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie Sie sie hier vorschlagen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "55.763", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "55.764", 
   "id": "s000124", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nicht beantworten werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "55.764", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "55.765", 
   "id": "s000125", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir brauchen endlich eine Vergleichbarkeit bei den Schulabschl\u00fcssen der Bundesl\u00e4nder. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "55.765", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "55.766", 
   "id": "s000126", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diese erreichen wir durch diese Grundgesetz\u00e4nderung nicht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "55.766", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "55.767", 
   "id": "s000127", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir brauchen einheitliche Bildungsstandards in ganz Deutschland, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "55.767", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "55.768", 
   "id": "s000128", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und zwar verbindliche Bildungsstandards f\u00fcr alle 16\u00a0Bundesl\u00e4nder. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "55.768", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "55.769", 
   "id": "s000129", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Daran probiert sich die Kultusministerkonferenz schon seit Jahren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "55.769", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "55.770", 
   "id": "s000130", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber es gelingt ihr nicht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "55.770", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "55.771", 
   "id": "s000131", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Daher wirbt die CDU/CSU-Fraktion f\u00fcr einen Staatsvertrag, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "55.771", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "56.600", 
   "id": "s000132", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der von den Ministerpr\u00e4sidenten geschlossen wird und der verbindliche Standards festlegt und sich dabei nat\u00fcrlich am leistungsst\u00e4rksten Bundesland orientiert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "56.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "56.640", 
   "id": "s000133", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Ganze funktioniert schon gut. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "56.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "56.920", 
   "id": "s000134", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir sehen das im Rundfunkrecht beim Rundfunkstaatsvertrag. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "56.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "57.480", 
   "id": "s000135", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch hier haben wir ein f\u00f6derales System. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "57.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "57.600", 
   "id": "s000136", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Hier tragen die L\u00e4nder Verantwortung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "57.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "57.760", 
   "id": "s000137", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es gelingt ihnen hier, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "57.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "58.240", 
   "id": "s000138", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "bundeseinheitlich t\u00e4tig zu werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "58.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "60.200", 
   "id": "s000139", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im \u00dcbrigen eint uns das Ziel bez\u00fcglich der Bildungsstandards \u00fcber Parteigrenzen hinweg."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "60.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "60.280", 
   "id": "s000140", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Lassen Sie mich abschlie\u00dfend festhalten: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "60.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "60.281", 
   "id": "s000141", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nach den Erfahrungen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "60.281", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "60.282", 
   "id": "s000142", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die wir im Bund mit den L\u00e4ndern insbesondere im Bildungsbereich gemacht haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "60.282", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "60.600", 
   "id": "s000143", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "steht f\u00fcr die Union fest: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "60.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "61.240", 
   "id": "s000144", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir geben keine unkonditionierten Mittel mehr in die Bundesl\u00e4nder. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "61.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "66.240", 
   "id": "s000145", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zus\u00e4tzliches finanzielles Engagement muss f\u00fcr den Bund mit inhaltlicher Gestaltungskompetenz einhergehen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "66.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "67.160", 
   "id": "s000146", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dieser Erfahrung und dieser Forderung sollten sich auch die anderen Fraktionen nicht verwehren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "67.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "68.360", 
   "id": "s000147", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Lassen Sie Ihre Vernunft wachsen!"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "68.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "72.000", 
   "id": "s000148", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Kollegin Saskia Esken hat das Wort zu einer Kurzintervention."
   ]
  }
 ]
}